{
  "stem": "17426.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the father was upset, obviously, terribly upset, and so was the mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they felt that now that daughter at best can only be a divorcee, because she had-- have to have a real divorce.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, she would have to live with this man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was quite below their status.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he asked the man to come back in the morning, and he'll straighten everything out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that came the second act, when he comes back in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the father sits down with this poor [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] halfwit, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he offers him money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, I don't want money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't need money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you want?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I want to be married to your daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now that they married me, I don't want to get a divorce.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course they were all besides themself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cannot force this man to divorce his daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they can also not allow him this daughter to live with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so as time went on, the daughter came in, and she started to listen to this man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were several scenes beyond this, in which she became more acquainted with him as a person, rather than as the halfwit that the town saw him [BACKROUND NOISE] and saw his real wisdom, his character, and his being as being a real fine person.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then she in the last act insists that her parents allow her to be married to the man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that is such a wonderful ending, such a nice ending, where rich and poor see one another not through the money and not through the riches but see one another through the soul and through the heart that they have.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
